# Project technology stack

- We use Python 3.13
- We use discord.py
- We make heavy use of LLM calls using async calls
- Please always follow the pythonic way of writing code

## Project purpose

This project is a Discord bot to utilise LLM's via API calls to let Discord users interact with the bot in
a natural way.  The bot has various tools it can call on, such as weather forecasts, image generation, web-page
summarisation.

